## 📱 About

**TASystem** is an offline-first Android mobile application developed by the
**RICTU 12 ICT Unit** of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources
Region XII (DENR XII).

It is designed to help ICT Support Staff manage and track Technical Assistance
(TA) requests from client offices — even without internet connection.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 **Secure Login** — Online and offline authentication
- 📊 **Dashboard** — Real-time ticket statistics with custom filters
- 🎫 **Ticket Management** — Create and resolve support tickets
- ✍️ **Digital Signatures** — Client and staff signature capture
- 📷 **Photo Capture** — Attach photo evidence to resolutions
- 📵 **Offline Mode** — Full functionality without internet
- 🔄 **Auto Sync** — Automatically syncs data when server is back online
- 🔔 **OTA Updates** — Over-the-air app updates

