---

## 🔄 How to Update

1. Open TASystem app
2. Go to **About** page from sidebar
3. Tap **Check for Updates**
4. If update is available tap **Update Now**
5. Follow installation instructions

The app also **automatically checks** for updates on startup.

---

## 📋 Requirements

| Requirement | Details |
|-------------|---------|
| Platform | Android |
| Android Version | 10 (API 29) or higher |
| Storage | Minimum 50MB free |
| Permissions | Camera, Storage |
| Network | WiFi or Mobile Data (for online mode) |

---

## 🗄️ Database

| Item | Details |
|------|---------|
| Online DB | Microsoft SQL Server |
| Offline DB | SQLite (on device) |
| Database | TAS |

