## 📂 Repository Structure

```
tasystem-releases/
├── README.md          ← This file
├── version.json       ← Current version info for OTA updates
└── releases/          ← APK files (via GitHub Releases)
```

---

## 🔧 For Developers — Release Process

1. Update `CurrentVersion` and `CurrentVersionCode` in `UpdateService.cs`
2. Build Release APK in Visual Studio
3. Create new GitHub Release with tag `v{version}`
4. Upload APK to the release
5. Update `version.json` with new version info and APK URL

### version.json format:
```json
{
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "versionCode": 1,
  "releaseNotes": "What changed in this version",
  "apkUrl": "https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/tasystem-releases/releases/download/v1.0.0/TASystem.apk",
  "forceUpdate": false
}
```

